  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Levanna is offered on a half board basis.</p>
<p>Fuel up for the day at the varied breakfast buffet with a classic continental offering with additional hot options. You can enjoy a selection of <span>pastries, breads, fresh fruits, cereals, as well as meat and cheese boards.</span></p>
<p>You can enjoy a tasty three course meal in the Les Terrasses restaurant, you have the choice of menu <span>with an emphasis on sharing and dishes skilfully prepared over an open fire. As part of the half-board option, you can also enjoy dinner in a few of the nearby Etincelles restaurants including Le Chalet, Aiguille Percee Restaurant, and La Brasserie de l’Arbina. Please enquire with the reception for availability, and to book a table. </span></p>
<p>Christmas and New Year gala dinner included on half board. </p>]]></cateringDescription>
