  <description><![CDATA[<p>This hotel has probably the best location in <a data-udi="umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565" href="/{localLink:umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565}" title="Tignes">Tignes</a> le Lac with doorstep skiing, and a lot of great piste choices. The Tovière gondola is less than a minute's walk away (30m) and the resort leisure centre with pool is just across the piste, the free resort bus stops just outside making it really easy to hop on and see the other villages.</p>
<h2>Piste side location</h2>
<p>The Levanna is a cosy and stylish hotel ideally located a snowball's throw from the Tovières ski lift. You have access to a variety of slopes, and can access the wider <a data-udi="umb://document/3f107aa9435442a892636b72e6e40b03" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3f107aa9435442a892636b72e6e40b03}" title="Tignes-Val d’Isere Ski Area">Tignes-Val d'Isere Ski Area</a> which is included in the full area pass. When you return from a day of skiing, the ski room features heated boot warmers and lockers. </p>
<h2>Food and drink</h2>
<p>The sun terrace outside has amazing views of the piste and Grande Motte Glacier - it is a great spot to soak up the winter sun. Warm up at the hotel with a hot chocolate, spiced mulled wine, or perhaps a glass of wine. There's also a lounge with billiards and a fireplace, which creates a relaxed environment after a day on the slopes.<span> </span></p>
<p><span>As part of the half-board option at the Levanna, you can enjoy dinner in Les Terrasses restaurant which serves tasty seasonal produce and charcole dishes. You also have the option to dine around in a few of the nearby Etincelles restaurants - enjoy bistro style dishes at Le Chalet, sample Savoyard specialities at La Brasserie de l’Arbina or head to Aiguille Percee Restaurant for local gourmet cuisine.  </span>If you fancy dining in any of these restaurants, speak to the reception team to book a table. </p>
<h2>Soothing spa and relaxation</h2>
<p>After a long day of skiing (or relaxing), you can unwind at the spa and wellness area which features a sauna, hammam and hot tub - perfect for soothing achy ski legs. In addition, you can book a treatment or massage locally.</p>
<p> </p>]]></description>
