  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Comfort Village Rooms</strong> sleep one to two people and are around 16<span>m²</span>. These rooms have twin beds, a shower and a balcony with village views.</p>
<p><strong>Comfort Mountain Rooms</strong> sleep one to two people and are around 19<span>m²</span>. These rooms have twin beds, a shower and a balcony with mountain views.</p>
<p><strong>Privilege Rooms</strong> sleep two to three people and are around 24<span>m². These rooms have twin beds, and an additional sofa bed,  shower or bath and a mountain or village view from the balcony.</span></p>
<p><span><strong>Duplex Suites</strong> sleep four to five people and are around 40m². These rooms have twin beds downstairs, twin beds on the mezzanine, and an additional sofa bed. There's a shower and bathroom, lounge area and balcony with mountain views.</span></p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Room facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><span>Balcony </span></li>
<li><span>Mountain or lake view</span></li>
<li><span>TV</span></li>
<li><span>Telephone</span></li>
<li><span>Safe</span></li>
<li><span>Wi-Fi</span></li>
<li><span>Hairdryer</span></li>
<li><span>Bath or shower </span></li>
<li><span>Cots are available on request</span></li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
